Scope

This file contains every private tag entry in group (0013,xxxx) that appears in the master
spreadsheet. Use it as the authoritative reference when embedding or validating DICOCH
metadata in your DICOM files.

Format
------
    (0013,EEEE) VR "Keyword"

0013  -- reserved private group for Digital Imaging & Communications for Cultural Heritage (DICOCH).
EEEE  -- element number as four-digit hexadecimal.
VR    -- Value Representation.
Keyword -- tag name.
